<br>
<br>Beautiful 4bd, 2.5ba two-story condo, with approximately 1,474 sqft. Newly refurbished unit, with new luxury vinyl plank flooring, new carpet, new paint, new doors and hardware, new quartz counter tops, new dishwasher, new bathroom vanity, and more! Double pane windows and central heating and air conditioning throughout. Large kitchen/dining combo comes with quartz counter tops, electric range, dishwasher, and garbage disposal. Tenants can bring their own fridge, washer, and dryer. Laundry room has electric hookup. Half bathroom downstairs. Luxury vinyl plank flooring all throughout, with exception of the carpet on the stairs. Primary bathroom has a wide shower stall. Upstairs hall bathroom has a shower-tub combo. Private patio has a storage closet, and leads out to the carport. Two parking spaces are assigned to this unit. Open guest parking, as well as street parking available for additional vehicles and guests. Convenient commuters location; off North Capitol Ave, near 680 and Berryessa Rd. Less than one mile to the VTA Hostetter and Berryessa Light Rail Stations. Plenty of shopping and dining nearby, with just one mile to the Safeway shopping center. Three major parks within 2 miles. Penitencia Creek Park offers a playground, pond, trails, a track, and baseball and softball fields. Flickinger Park offers community space with a softball field, 2 basketball courts, horseshoe pits, and picnic areas. Cataldi Park offers lawns &amp; tree-shaded trails, 8 tennis courts, and a handball court.
